// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-3361 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 05296489-5399-5008-8642-0ae0edb2ea97

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
